      "text": "Fabric SQL Database Audit\n- A Fabric SQL Database for Audit purposes\n\n\nrole_creation_audit_tbl\nPurpose:  Keep track of all roles created for auditing purposes\nschema\n[\ndate: datetime:  Time the role creation job was run\nfile_name: str:  Name of the yml file run\npipeline_id: int:  The data pipeline that ran the job\nprincipal_id: int:  The principal id that ran the job\nall the parameters from the yml file (still need to determine all the parameters and that file's structure)\n]\n\n\n\nrole_mapping_audit_tbl\nPurpose:  Keep track of all users added to roles for auditing purposes\nschema\n[\ndate: datetime:  Time the role creation job was run\nfile_name: str:  Name of the yml file run\npipeline_id: int:  The data pipeline that ran the job\nprincipal_id: int:  The principal id that ran the job\nall the parameters from the yml file (still need to determine all the parameters and that file's structure)\n]",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Fabric SQL Database Audit\n- A Fabric SQL Database for Audit purposes\n\n\nrole_creation_audit_tbl\nPurpose:  Keep track of all roles created for auditing purposes\nschema\n[\ndate: datetime:  Time the role creation job was run\nfile_name: str:  Name of the yml file run\npipeline_id: int:  The data pipeline that ran the job\nprincipal_id: int:  The principal id that ran the job\nall the parameters from the yml file (still need to determine all the parameters and that file's structure)\n]\n\n\n\nrole_mapping_audit_tbl\nPurpose:  Keep track of all users added to roles for auditing purposes\nschema\n[\ndate: datetime:  Time the role creation job was run\nfile_name: str:  Name of the yml file run\npipeline_id: int:  The data pipeline that ran the job\nprincipal_id: int:  The principal id that ran the job\nall the parameters from the yml file (still need to determine all the parameters and that file's structure)\n]",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
